  import React, { useState } from 'react';

  const PlayerStats = () => {
      const [searchTerm1, setSearchTerm1] = useState('');
      const [searchTerm2, setSearchTerm2] = useState('');
      
      const players = [
          {
              name: "LeBron James",
              team: "Los Angeles Lakers",
              img: "img/lebronsunshinecover.jpg"
          },
          {
              name: "Chet Holmgren",
              team: "Oklahoma City Thunder",
              img: "img/oklahomacitythunder/chetholmgren.png"
          },
          // Add more players as needed
      ];
      
      const handleSearch1 = (event) => {
          setSearchTerm1(event.target.value);
      };
      
      const handleSearch2 = (event) => {
          setSearchTerm2(event.target.value);
      };
  
      const filteredPlayer1 = players.find(player =>
          player.name.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm1.toLowerCase())
      );
  
      const filteredPlayer2 = players.find(player =>
          player.name.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm2.toLowerCase())
      );
  
      return (
          <header>
              <h1>Compare Players</h1>
              <p>Compare the stats of two NBA players side by side.</p>
              <main>
                  <div className="flex-container">
                      <section>
                          <div className="card-container">
                              <div className="section">
                                  <form>
                                      <div className="search">
                                          <input
                                              className="search-input"
                                              type="text"
                                              placeholder="Search for a player..."
                                              value={searchTerm1}
                                              onChange={handleSearch1}
                                          />
                                      </div>
                                  </form>
                                  {filteredPlayer1 ? (
                                      <>
                                          <img src={filteredPlayer1.img} alt={`${filteredPlayer1.name} Meme`} />
                                          <p>{filteredPlayer1.name} - {filteredPlayer1.team}</p>
                                      </>
                                  ) : (
                                      <p>No player found</p>
                                  )}
                              </div>
                              <div className="section comparison-section">
                                  <h3 style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>Player Stats Compared (2024)</h3>
                                  <Comparison />
                              </div>
                              <div className="section">
                                  <form>
                                      <div className="search">
                                          <input
                                              className="search-input"
                                              type="text"
                                              placeholder="Search for a player..."
                                              value={searchTerm2}
                                              onChange={handleSearch2}
                                          />
                                      </div>
                                  </form>
                                  {filteredPlayer2 ? (
                                      <>
                                          <img src={filteredPlayer2.img} alt={`${filteredPlayer2.name} Meme`} />
                                          <p>{filteredPlayer2.name} - {filteredPlayer2.team}</p>
                                      </>
                                  ) : (
                                      <p>No player found</p>
                                  )}
                              </div>
                          </div>
                      </section>
                  </div>
              </main>
          </header>
      );
  };
  
  export default PlayerStats;
